{"tid":2158210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"維記牛奶疑隱瞞員工確診支那肺炎 跟車工人染疫廠房未有關閉消毒","createTime":"2020-08-15T14:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T04:25:00.000Z","uid":236891,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99d483e6413b5b06d87ca605dc2696abd549959f","tid":2158210,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/STFQXXFQEBBD7FDFNF636BGW6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FSTFQXXFQEBBD7FDFNF636BGW6A%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL8WiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=5fff93bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FSTFQXXFQEBBD7FDFNF636BGW6A%2F&h=b4c85fac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/STFQXXFQEBBD7FDFNF636BGW6A/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》接獲讀者爆料指，維記牛奶（THE KOWLOON DAIRY）有員工確診武漢肺炎，並有12名密切接觸同事送往駿洋邨隔離檢疫，惟廠房封鎖消息，令上下員工十分擔心。衞生署向《蘋果》證實該公司有1名跟車送貨員工確診武漢肺炎。發言人接受查詢時表示，染病為1名59歲男子（第4373號個案），屬署方今日（15日）公佈個案，《蘋果》已向維記牛奶查詢，相關跟進工作，正等候回覆。<br />\n<br />\n爆料人士指出，共有12名與確診患者有緊密接觸的員工已送往駿洋邨檢疫。惟今日廠房仍照舊如常運作，該公司沒有關閉廠房消毒，令員工很擔心。公司內部也封鎖有關同事染疫的消息，不准員工討論事件。<br />\n<br />\n貼咗一部份新聞，其他自己比錢睇"},{"pid":"636b7282f531bdb6fc753f5592444d9a7601ee2f","tid":2158210,"uid":49532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T14:37:16.000Z","msg":"香港人條命真係賤過狗<br />\n賤種老細淨係諗點樣繼續搵錢"},{"pid":"daafe217e57ef0f9f63e1051c32f213177c771ab","tid":2158210,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T15:03:23.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"268e79b5251b40b4a6467dab0a6547a9a2405021","tid":2158210,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"The Wuhan Dairy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b0412b5308e1c605ee525327e43c1bf72244c8","tid":2158210,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"樓主貼堂作品: A0狗  100%狙擊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXevSbg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXevSbg.png&h=ad7644c8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}